			</a>
		</article>
		<article class="featured-thumb">
			<a href="http://tioki.com/groups/632-building-excellent-schools" target="_blank">
				<img src="/assets/tioki/ourcustomers/BES.png" alt="" style="width:150px"/>
			</a>
		</article>
		<article class="featured-thumb">
			<a href="http://tioki.com/groups/279-green-dot-public-schools" target="_blank">
				<img src="/assets/tioki/ourcustomers/green_dot.png" alt="" style="width:150px"/>
